GPT Specific:

The "Forge" Quick Start
Create a New GPT: Go to "Explore GPTs" and click + Create.

Configure the "Brain": * Click the Configure tab.

Paste the entire text of Forge_Skill.md into the Instructions box. This gives the AI the "rules" of how to think and remember.

Create the "Memory": * Scroll down to Knowledge.

Upload your Forge_Index.md file. (Even if it is blank, this is the "seed").

Enable the "Tools": * Ensure Code Interpreter is checked (this helps the AI parse and search your Index file more deeply).

Begin: Click Create/Update in the top right.
